    <h1>Sustainability</h1> 
    <div id="left_col"> 
     <p id="intro">Cornell supports research, scholarship, and the practical application of knowledge that address one of humankind's greatest challenges: achieving a sustainable world for all.</p> 
     <h2 id="feature_heading">Emerging Ideas in Sustainability</h2> 
     <div id="feature">
      <a href="http://news.cornell.edu/stories/2014/12/cornell-buy-all-proposed-black-oak-wind-farms-energy"><img src="http://www.cornell.edu/sustainability/img/20150227-Recyclemania-428x243.jpg" width="428" height="243" alt="Students guide recycling"></a> 
      <h3> RECYCLEMANIA 2015 - Let the Games Begin!</h3> 
      <p>From February to March, Cornell students will compete with <a href="http://r5.fs.cornell.edu/mania/default.cfm">colleges across the US and Canada</a> to see who recycles the most per capita and the highest percentage of total waste. Email <a href="mailto:recycle@cornell.edu">recycle@cornell.edu</a> and pledge to use a reusable mug through March 28th, and you might win a $20 gift card to the Cornell Store.</p> 
     </div> 
    </div>
    <!-- END left_col --> 
    <div id="right_col"> 
     <div id="tab_area"> 
      <ul id="tab_nav"> 
       <li class="selected"><a href="#" class="tab" id="researchTab">Research</a></li> 
